data.description: Welcome to your future home on Genevieve Dr in this quiet Menifee neighborhood! This stunning house has charm that will captivate you. This single story home features 2 bedroom 1 bath which is perfect for a first-time buyer or someone that is downsizing. For added flexibility, there's an optional room providing versatility to accommodate various needs.   The landscaping features automatic sprinkler system front & back, planters, and trees, creating an inviting atmosphere. The backyard features a block retaining wall, concrete, and patio cover which offers a perfect space for relaxation or a family barbeque.   Inside, you'll find a home adorned with an open concept, vinyl windows, quarts kitchen counter tops adding to its undeniable charm. Noteworthy is the absence of any HOA fees making this home the ideal choice.  Take note of the recent improvements – the furnace and water heater ensuring efficiency and comfort. The inclusion of solar panels, with a manageable monthly payment under a solar purchase agreement, adds an eco-friendly touch to the home.
